            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Как мы можем повторно использовать созданную f-строку?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Мы сохраняем это в <code>variable</code> и используем <code>variable</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Мы не можем повторно использовать f-строки</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Мы сохраняем это в <code>variable</code> и используем <code>variable</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: f-strings",
            "id": 78997,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Отобразите f-string.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;\" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" dataset entries&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"28\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;4 dataset entries&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"4 dataset entries\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>f\"{4} dataset entries\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: The character f",
            "id": 78998,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Добавь символ <code>f</code> перед форматированной строкой.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;popularity increased by \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"12\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\"%&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"7\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"popularity increased by 12%\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>f</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Curly braces for values",
            "id": 78999,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Отобразите <code>500</code> внутри строки, закодировав <code>{500}</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;I would walk \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text value=\"500\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\" miles&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"26\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"I would walk 500 miles\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>{500}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Variables",
            "id": 79001,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Отобрази текущую температуру, закодировав <code>degrees</code> в фигурных скобках.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"degrees = \" /><text value=\"70\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Temperature: \" /><text value=\"{degrees}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"F&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"34\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"42\" /><option startIndex=\"42\" endIndex=\"43\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"print\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Temperature: 70F\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>{</code>, затем <code>degrees</code>, и наконец <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
