            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Сохрани f-строку в переменной <code>display</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"movie = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Vertigo&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"display = \" /><text value=\"f&quot;Airing tonight: \" /><text value=\"{movie}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(display)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"28\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"54\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Airing tonight: Vertigo\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>display</code>, затем <code>=</code>, а затем <code>f</code>, <code>\"Airing tonight: {movie}\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
